name: Dynareign
description:
Dynareign is a game i made in 5 days to challenge myself, however im more than happy to keep working on it and turn it into a full game in enough people enjoy it and want to see more.

Feedback would be greatly appreciated so i know where i can improve on in the future, and if you want to see more of Dynareign let me know in the comments or by rating the game, Thanks =)
